<br>
Healing pet at 18% yielded 257% after CH (almost every time, I have about 20 points between 15% and 30% and results are very consistent).  CH always does 10,000 hp.  So here is the math:<br>
<br>
a = start health %<br>
b = result health %<br>
x = pet HP<br>
H = heal points<br>
<br>
a * x / 100  + H  = b * x / 100  (basic math here, health before + CH = health after)<br>
<br>
a * x + 100 * H = b * x    (*100 to remove 2 divisions)<br>
<br>
b * x - a * x = 100 * H   (subtract -a*x from both sides)<br>
<br>
x = (100 * H) / (b - a)    (solve for x)<br>
<br>
